OL,3,CHome 'blasted with rocks' as burst
OL,4,Cpipe shoots water and debris into the
OL,5,Csky
OL,7,FWatch as thousands of litres of water
OL,8,Fa second are sprayed high into the sky.
OL,10,FA home in Gloucestershire has been
OL,11,Fdamaged after a burst water main shot
OL,12,Fdebris and thousands of litres of
OL,13,Fwater in the air.
OL,15,FIt happened near Sneedhams Road in
OL,16,FGloucester on the morning of Wednesday
OL,17,F14 May.
