OL,7,FThose living nearby reported hearing a
OL,8,Fcracking sound in the moments before.
OL,9,FThe ground has also been torn apart by
OL,10,Fwater pressure.
OL,12,FSevern Trent Water engineers are at
OL,13,Fthe scene, and Gloucestershire Fire
OL,14,Fand Rescue Service is assisting the
OL,15,Foperation.
OL,17,FOn X, Gloucestershire Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService said: "There is a reported
OL,19,Fwater main break occurring near the
OL,20,Fintersection of Sneedhams Rd and
OL,21,FWinnycroft Lane.
