OL,7,F"Gloucestershire Fire and Rescue are
OL,8,Fon scene, as is Severn Trent Water.
OL,9,FSTW is evaluating the situation,
OL,10,Ffurther updates to follow."
OL,12,FCommunity Independent Councillor
OL,13,FAlastair Chambers (Matson, Robinswood
OL,14,Fand White City) has commented on the
OL,15,Fsituation. He said: "Unbelievable,
OL,16,Fthousands of litres of water a second
OL,17,Fare being sprayed 100ft in the air.
