OL,3,CHome 'blasted with rocks' as burst
OL,4,Cpipe shoots water and debris into the
OL,5,Csky
OL,7,F"Concrete, earth and debris have
OL,8,Fspraying out the ground. Inches of
OL,9,Fthick concrete slab blown out in huge
OL,10,Fchunks.
OL,12,F"And sadly the million-pound home next
OL,13,Fto the water main in lovely condition
OL,14,Fhas been blasted with rocks and debris
OL,15,Fbreaking windows and roof tiles."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for Gloucestershire
OL,18,FFire and Rescue Service said: "We were
OL,19,Fcalled at 6.18am to a burst water main
OL,20,Fin Sneedhams Road, in Matson,
OL,21,FGloucester.
