OL,7,F"One fire engine, from Gloucester
OL,8,FSouth, was sent to the scene where we
OL,9,Fhelped to make the scene safe.
OL,11,F"The incident has now been handed over
OL,12,Fto Severn Trent Water. The stop
OL,13,Fmessage was received at 8.31am.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Severn Trent said:
OL,16,F"Our teams have now massively reduced
OL,17,Fthe burst in Matson, so it is now no
OL,18,Flonger visible.
